{"word":"G1299 - διατάσσω - diatássō - dee-at-as'-so - Appoint","slug":"G1299","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">διατάσσω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>diatássō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>dee-at-as'-so"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Appoint"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03B4;&#x03B9;&#x03B1;&#x03C4;&#x03B1;&#x0301;&#x03C3;&#x03C3;&#x03C9; - diatasso&#x0304;</b> - <i>dee-at-as'-so</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G1223\">G1223</a> and <a href=\"#/G5021\">G5021</a>; to <i>arrange thoroughly</i>, that is, (specifically) <i>institute</i>, <i>prescribe</i>, etc.: - appoint, command, give, (set in) order, ordain."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1296\">G1296</a>, <a href=\"#/G1297\">G1297</a>, <a href=\"#/G2004\">G2004</a>, <a href=\"#/G392\">G392</a>, <a href=\"#/G4367\">G4367</a>, <a href=\"#/G5001\">G5001</a>, <a href=\"#/G5021\">G5021</a>, <a href=\"#/G506\">G506</a>, <a href=\"#/G5292\">G5292</a>, <a href=\"#/G5293\">G5293</a>, <a href=\"#/G657\">G657</a>, <a href=\"#/G812\">G812</a>, <a href=\"#/G813\">G813</a>, <a href=\"#/G814\">G814</a>"}]}